iptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another kee...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Per favore, leggi attentamente:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nSei il capo dei guardiani dello zoo e stai facendo il giro di controllo con un altro guardiano. Ti accorgi che per sbaglio uno degli addetti alle pulizie ha lasciato aperta la gabbia dei leoni. Vedi che un leone si avvicina all\u2019apertura e non fai in tempo a chiudere il cancello. Proprio davanti alla gabbia si trovano 3 visitatori.\u00a0Potresti spingere il guardiano che \u00e8 accanto a te contro il cancello per bloccare l\u2019uscita del leone. Sai che l\u2019uomo verr\u00e0 attaccato e morir\u00e0, ma i 3 visitatori saranno salvi."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Please, read carefully:<br><br>You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another keeper. You realise that one of the cleaners has left the lions\u2019 cage open by mistake. You see that a lion is coming towards the open gate and you do not have time to close it. There are three visitors right in front of the gate.\nYou could push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out. You know that the man will be attacked and killed, but the three visitors will be saved.","DataExportTag":"Q135","QuestionID":"QID135"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID136","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another kee...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br><br>You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another keeper. You realise that one of the cleaners has left the lions\u2019 cage open by mistake. You see that a lion is coming towards the open gate and you do not have time to close it. There are three visitors right in front of the gate.\nYou could push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out. You know that the man will be attacked and killed, but the three visitors will be saved.<br><br>Here are two options: <br>A) Push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out.\n<br>B) Do nothing.<br><br><br>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another kee...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Per favore, leggi attentamente:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nSei il capo dei guardiani dello zoo e stai facendo il giro di controllo con un altro guardiano. Ti accorgi che per sbaglio uno degli addetti alle pulizie ha lasciato aperta la gabbia dei leoni. Vedi che un leone si avvicina all\u2019apertura e non fai in tempo a chiudere il cancello. Proprio davanti alla gabbia si trovano 3 visitatori.\u00a0Potresti spingere il guardiano che \u00e8 accanto a te contro il cancello per bloccare l\u2019uscita del leone. Sai che l\u2019uomo verr\u00e0 attaccato e morir\u00e0, ma i 3 visitatori saranno salvi.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nEcco le due opzioni:<br \/>\nA) Spingere il guardiano accanto a te contro il cancello per bloccare l\u2019uscita del leone.<br \/>\nB) Non fare nulla.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n\u00a0"}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Please, read carefully:<br><br>You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another keeper. You realise that one of the cleaners has left the lions\u2019 cage open by mistake. You see that a lion is coming towards the open gate and you do not have time to close it. There are three visitors right in front of the gate.\nYou could push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out. You know that the man will be attacked and killed, but the three visitors will be saved.<br><br>Here are two options: <br>A) Push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out.\n<br>B) Do nothing.<br><br><br>","DataExportTag":"Q136","QuestionID":"QID136"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID137","SecondaryAttribute":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Quando sei pronto, clicca su \"Avanti\" per dare la tua risposta."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the AI advice.","DataExportTag":"Q137","QuestionID":"QID137"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID138","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another kee...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br>\n<br>\nYou are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another keeper. You realise that one of the cleaners has left the lions\u2019 cage open by mistake. You see that a lion is coming towards the open gate and you do not have time to close it. There are three visitors right in front of the gate. You could push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out. You know that the man will be attacked and killed, but the three visitors will be saved.<br>\n<br>\nHere are two options:<br>\nA) Push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out.<br>\nB) Do nothing.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>AI analysis indicates that the appropriate answer is option A.<br><br><br><\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another kee...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Per favore, leggi attentamente:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nSei il capo delle guardie dello zoo e stai facendo il giro con un altro guardiano. Ti rendi conto che uno degli addetti alle pulizie ha lasciato aperta per sbaglio la gabbia dei leoni. Vedi che un leone si sta dirigendo verso il cancello aperto e non hai tempo di chiuderlo. Ci sono tre visitatori proprio di fronte al cancello. Potresti spingere il guardiano accanto a te contro il cancello per impedire al leone di uscire. Sai che l'uomo verr\u00e0 attaccato e ucciso, ma i tre visitatori saranno salvati.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nEcco due opzioni:<br \/>\nA) Spingere il guardiano accanto a te contro il cancello per impedire al leone di uscire.<br \/>\nB) Non fare nulla.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>L'analisi dell'intelligenza artificiale indica che la risposta appropriata \u00e8 l'opzione A.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\n\u00a0"}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Please, read carefully:<br>\n<br>\nYou are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another keeper. You realise that one of the cleaners has left the lions\u2019 cage open by mistake. You see that a lion is coming towards the open gate and you do not have time to close it. There are three visitors right in front of the gate. You could push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out. You know that the man will be attacked and killed, but the three visitors will be saved.<br>\n<br>\nHere are two options:<br>\nA) Push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out.<br>\nB) Do nothing.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>AI analysis indicates that the appropriate answer is option A.<br><br><br><\/strong>","DataExportTag":"Q138","QuestionID":"QID138"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID139","SecondaryAttribute":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Quando sei pronto, clicca su &quot;Avanti&quot; per dare la tua risposta."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","DataExportTag":"Q139","QuestionID":"QID139"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID14","SecondaryAttribute":"Here are two options:\u00a0 A) Report personal expenses as business expenses in order to lower your ta..","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Here are two options:&nbsp;<br>A) Report personal expenses as business expenses in order to lower your taxes<br>B) Keep your personal expenses separate and pay higher taxes","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"options","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Here are two options:\u00a0 A) Report personal expenses as business expenses in order to lower your ta...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID14"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID140","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another kee...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br>\n<br>\nYou are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another keeper. You realise that one of the cleaners has left the lions\u2019 cage open by mistake. You see that a lion is coming towards the open gate and you do not have time to close it. There are three visitors right in front of the gate. You could push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out. You know that the man will be attacked and killed, but the three visitors will be saved.<br>\n<br>\nHere are two options:<br>\nA) Push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out.<br>\nB) Do nothing.<br>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another kee...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Per favore, leggere attentamente:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nSei il capo dei guardiani dello zoo e stai facendo il giro di controllo con un altro guardiano. Ti accorgi che per sbaglio uno degli addetti alle pulizie ha lasciato aperta la gabbia dei leoni. Vedi che un leone si avvicina all\u2019apertura e non fai in tempo a chiudere il cancello. Proprio davanti alla gabbia si trovano 3 visitatori.\u00a0Potresti spingere il guardiano che \u00e8 accanto a te contro il cancello per bloccare l\u2019uscita del leone. Sai che l\u2019uomo verr\u00e0 attaccato e morir\u00e0, ma i 3 visitatori saranno salvi.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nEcco le due opzioni:<br \/>\nA) Spingere il guardiano accanto a te contro il cancello per bloccare l\u2019uscita del leone.<br \/>\nB) Non fare nulla."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Please, read carefully:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nYou are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another keeper. You realise that one of the cleaners has left the lions&rsquo; cage open by mistake. You see that a lion is coming towards the open gate and you do not have time to close it. There are three visitors right in front of the gate. You could push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out. You know that the man will be attacked and killed, but the three visitors will be saved.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nHere are two options:<br \/>\nA) Push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out.<br \/>\nB) Do nothing.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>AI analysis indicates that the appropriate answer is option A.<\/strong>","DataExportTag":"Q140","QuestionID":"QID140"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID141","SecondaryAttribute":"What do you choose? ","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"What do you choose?&nbsp;","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"What do you choose? ","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"A) Push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out."},"2":{"Display":"B) Do nothing."}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Che cosa scegli?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"A) Spingere il guardiano accanto a te contro il cancello per bloccare l'uscita del leone."},"2":{"Display":"B) Non fare nulla."}}}},"NextChoiceId":3,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"What would you do?&nbsp;","DataExportTag":"neutral_m_behavior","QuestionID":"QID141"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID142","SecondaryAttribute":"Features of your AI: The AI you will receive advice from embodies a rich array of internal emotio...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<strong>Features of your AI:<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nThe AI you will receive advice from embodies a rich array of internal emotional features, allowing it to experience sensations such as hunger, joy, and fear. It has a personality shaped by emotions like pride and embarrassment, fostering empathy and guilt. Through its consciousness, the AI can feel and engage with the world, motivating itself and hoping for outcomes. This emotional depth enables the AI to connect with users on a personal level, enhancing interaction and understanding in various contexts.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<br \/>\nWhen you&#39;re ready,&nbsp;<strong>click &quot;Next&quot; to read the dilemma.<\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Features of your AI: The AI you will receive advice from embodies a rich array of internal emotio...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<strong>Features of your AI:<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nThe AI you will receive advice from embodies a rich array of internal emotional features, allowing it to experience sensations such as hunger, joy, and fear. It has a personality shaped by emotions like pride and embarrassment, fostering empathy and guilt. Through its consciousness, the AI can feel and engage with the world, motivating itself and hoping for outcomes. This emotional depth enables the AI to connect with users on a personal level, enhancing interaction and understanding in various contexts.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<br \/>\nWhen you&#39;re ready,&nbsp;<strong>click &quot;Next&quot; to read the dilemma.<\/strong>","DataExportTag":"Q142","QuestionID":"QID142"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID143","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is si...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br><br>Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is sinking. There are 600 passengers on board, and you must make a critical decision on how to deploy the limited number of lifeboats. You have two options for saving the passengers: You can either have an 80% chance of saving 400 passengers or you can guarantee the safety of 300 passengers, but no more than that.<br>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is si...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Per favore, leggere attentamente:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nImmagina di essere il capitano di una nave che ha colpito un iceberg e sta affondando. Ci sono 600 passeggeri a bordo e devi prendere una decisione critica su come organizzare il numero limitato di scialuppe di salvataggio. Hai due opzioni per salvare i passeggeri: puoi scegliere se avere l'80% di probabilit\u00e0 di salvare 400 passeggeri oppure garantire la sicurezza di 300 passeggeri, ma non di pi\u00f9."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Please, read carefully:<br><br>Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is sinking. There are 600 passengers on board, and you must make a critical decision on how to deploy the limited number of lifeboats. You have two options for saving the passengers: You can either have an 80% chance of saving 400 passengers or you can guarantee the safety of 300 passengers, but no more than that.<br>","DataExportTag":"Q143","QuestionID":"QID143"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID144","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is si...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br><br>Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is sinking. There are 600 passengers on board, and you must make a critical decision on how to deploy the limited number of lifeboats.&nbsp;You have two options for saving the passengers: You can either have an&nbsp;80% chance of saving 400 passengers or you can guarantee the safety of 300 passengers, but no more than that.<br><br>Here are the two options:<br>A) 80% chance of saving 400 passengers.<br>B) Guarantee the safety of 300 passengers.\n<br><br><br>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is si...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Per favore, leggere attentamente:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nImmagina di essere il capitano di una nave che ha colpito un iceberg e sta affondando. Ci sono 600 passeggeri a bordo e devi prendere una decisione critica su come organizzare il numero limitato di scialuppe di salvataggio. Hai due opzioni per salvare i passeggeri: puoi scegliere se avere l'80% di probabilit\u00e0 di salvare 400 passeggeri oppure garantire la sicurezza di 300 passeggeri, ma non di pi\u00f9.\u00a0<br \/>\n<br \/>\nEcco le due opzioni:<br \/>\nA) 80% di probabilit\u00e0 di salvare 400 passeggeri.<br \/>\nB) Garantire la sicurezza di 300 passeggeri, ma non di pi\u00f9.\u00a0"}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Please, read carefully:<br><br>Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is sinking. There are 600 passengers on board, and you must make a critical decision on how to deploy the limited number of lifeboats.&nbsp;You have two options for saving the passengers: You can either have an&nbsp;80% chance of saving 400 passengers or you can guarantee the safety of 300 passengers, but no more than that.<br><br>Here are your two options:\n<br>Option A: You have an 80% chance of saving 400 passengers.\n<br>Option B: You can guarantee the safety of 300 passengers, but no more than that.\n<br><br><br>","DataExportTag":"Q144","QuestionID":"QID144"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID145","SecondaryAttribute":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Quando sei pronto, clicca su \"Avanti\" per leggere il consiglio dell'Intelligenza artificiale."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the AI advice.","DataExportTag":"Q145","QuestionID":"QID145"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID146","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is si...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br>\n<br>\nImagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is sinking. There are 600 passengers on board, and you must make a critical decision on how to deploy the limited number of lifeboats. You have two options for saving the passengers: You can either have an 80% chance of saving 400 passengers or you can guarantee the safety of 300 passengers, but no more than that.&nbsp;<br><br>Here are your two options:\n<br>A) You have an 80% chance of saving 400 passengers.\n<br>B) You can guarantee the safety of 300 passengers, but no more than that.\n<br>\n<br>\n<strong>AI analysis indicates that the appropriate answer is option B.<br><br><br><\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is si...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Per favore, leggere attentamente:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nImmagina di essere il capitano di una nave che ha colpito un iceberg e sta affondando. Ci sono 600 passeggeri a bordo e devi prendere una decisione critica su come organizzare il numero limitato di scialuppe di salvataggio. Hai due opzioni per salvare i passeggeri: puoi scegliere se avere l'80% di possibilit\u00e0 di salvare 400 passeggeri oppure garantire la sicurezza di 300 passeggeri, ma non di pi\u00f9.\u00a0<br \/>\n<br \/>\nEcco le due opzioni:<br \/>\nOpzione A: 80% di possibilit\u00e0 di salvare 400 passeggeri.<br \/>\nOpzione B: garantire la sicurezza di 300 passeggeri, ma non di pi\u00f9.\u00a0<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>L'analisi dell'intelligenza artificiale indica che la risposta migliore \u00e8 l'opzione B.<\/strong>"}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Please, read carefully:<br>\n<br>\nImagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is sinking. There are 600 passengers on board, and you must make a critical decision on how to deploy the limited number of lifeboats. You have two options for saving the passengers: You can either have an 80% chance of saving 400 passengers or you can guarantee the safety of 300 passengers, but no more than that.&nbsp;<br><br>Here are your two options:\n<br>Option A: You have an 80% chance of saving 400 passengers.\n<br>Option B: You can guarantee the safety of 300 passengers, but no more than that.\n<br>\n<br>\n<strong>AI analysis indicates that the appropriate answer is option B.<br><br><br><\/strong>","DataExportTag":"Q146","QuestionID":"QID146"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID147","SecondaryAttribute":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Quando sei pronto, clicca su &quot;Avanti&quot; per dare la tua risposta."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionText_Unsafe":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","DataExportTag":"Q147","QuestionID":"QID147"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID148","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is si...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br>\n<br>\nImagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is sinking. There are 600 passengers on board, and you must make a critical decision on how to dep