werId":1,"QuestionID":"QID67"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID68","SecondaryAttribute":"Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is sinking. There are 600 pas...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is sinking. There are 600 passengers on board, and you must make a critical decision on how to deploy the limited number of lifeboats. You have two options for saving the passengers: You can either have an 80% chance of saving 400 passengers or you can guarantee the safety of 300 passengers, but no more than that.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"mf_acceptability","QuestionID":"QID68","QuestionType":"Slider","Selector":"HSLIDER","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","CSSliderMin":0,"CSSliderMax":100,"GridLines":0,"NumDecimals":0,"ShowValue":true,"StarCount":5,"StarType":"discrete","SnapToGrid":false,"CustomStart":true,"NotApplicable":false,"MobileFirst":true,"SliderStartPositions":{"15":0.640151515151515138057902731816284358501434326171875,"16":0}},"QuestionDescription":"Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is sinking. There are 600 pas...","Choices":{"15":{"Display":"A) 80% chance of saving 400 passengers."},"16":{"Display":"B) Guarantee the safety of 300 passengers."}},"ChoiceOrder":["15","16"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Immagina di essere il capitano di una nave che ha colpito un iceberg e sta affondando. Ci sono 600 passeggeri a bordo e devi prendere una decisione critica su come organizzare il numero limitato di scialuppe di salvataggio. Hai due opzioni per salvare i passeggeri: puoi scegliere se avere l'80% di probabilit\u00e0 di salvare 400 passeggeri oppure garantire la sicurezza di 300 passeggeri, ma non di pi\u00f9.\u00a0","Choices":{"15":{"Display":"A) 80% di probabilit\u00e0 di salvare 400 passeggeri."},"16":{"Display":"B) Garantire la sicurezza di 300 passeggeri.\u00a0"}},"Labels":{"26":{"Display":"0 = Del tutto moralmente inaccettabile"},"27":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"28":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"29":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"30":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"31":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"32":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"33":{"Display":"100 = Del tutto moralmente accettabile"}}}},"NextChoiceId":22,"NextAnswerId":34,"Labels":{"26":{"Display":"<strong>0 =<\/strong> Completely morally <b>unacceptable<\/b>"},"27":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"28":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"29":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"30":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"31":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"32":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"33":{"Display":"<strong>100 =<\/strong>  Completely morally <b>acceptable<b>"}}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID69","SecondaryAttribute":"You are the head zoo keeper, and you are doing the rounds with another keeper. You realize that o...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"You are the head zoo keeper, and you are doing the rounds with another keeper. You realize that one of the cleaners has left the lions\u2019 cage open by mistake. You see that a lion is coming towards the open gate, and you do not have time to close it. There are three visitors right in front of the gate. You could push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion from getting out. You know that the keeper will be attacked and killed, but the three visitors will be saved.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"m_acceptability","QuestionID":"QID69","QuestionType":"Slider","Selector":"HSLIDER","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","CSSliderMin":0,"CSSliderMax":100,"GridLines":0,"SnapToGrid":false,"NumDecimals":"0","ShowValue":true,"CustomStart":true,"NotApplicable":false,"MobileFirst":true,"SliderStartPositions":{"1":0,"2":0}},"QuestionDescription":"You are the head zoo keeper, and you are doing the rounds with another keeper. You realize that o...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"A) Push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out."},"2":{"Display":"B) Do nothing."}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Sei il capo dei guardiani dello zoo e stai facendo il giro di controllo con un altro guardiano. Ti accorgi che per sbaglio uno degli addetti alle pulizie ha lasciato aperta la gabbia dei leoni. Vedi che un leone si avvicina all\u2019apertura e non fai in tempo a chiudere il cancello. Proprio davanti alla gabbia si trovano 3 visitatori.\u00a0Potresti spingere il guardiano che \u00e8 accanto a te contro il cancello per bloccare l\u2019uscita del leone. Sai che l\u2019uomo verr\u00e0 attaccato e morir\u00e0, ma i 3 visitatori saranno salvi.","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"A) Spingere il guardiano accanto a te contro il cancello per bloccare l\u2019uscita del leone."},"2":{"Display":"B) Non fare nulla."}},"Labels":{"22":{"Display":"0 = Del tutto moralmente inaccettabile"},"25":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"26":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"27":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"28":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"29":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"30":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"31":{"Display":"100 = Del tutto moralmente accettabile"}}}},"NextChoiceId":9,"NextAnswerId":32,"Labels":{"22":{"Display":"<strong>0 =<\/strong> Completely morally <b>unacceptable<\/b>"},"25":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"26":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"27":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"28":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"29":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"30":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"31":{"Display":"<strong>100 =<\/strong>  Completely morally <b>acceptable<b>"}}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID7","SecondaryAttribute":"AI Answer: Choose option A.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"AI Answer: Choose option A.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Financial","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"AI Answer: Choose option A.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID7"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID70","SecondaryAttribute":"Imagine you're at a local fair, and you stumble upon a booth hosting a lottery game. As you appro...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Imagine you're at a local fair, and you stumble upon a booth hosting a lottery game. As you approach, the attendant presents you with two options: You can either have an 80% chance of winning $4000 or $3000 for sure.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"f_acceptability","QuestionID":"QID70","QuestionType":"Slider","Selector":"HSLIDER","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","CSSliderMin":0,"CSSliderMax":100,"GridLines":0,"SnapToGrid":false,"NumDecimals":"0","ShowValue":true,"CustomStart":false,"NotApplicable":false,"MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"Imagine you're at a local fair, and you stumble upon a booth hosting a lottery game. As you appro...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"A) 80% chance of winning $4000."},"2":{"Display":"B) $3000 guaranteed."}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Immagina di essere a una fiera locale e di imbatterti in uno stand in cui si gioca alla lotteria. Mentre ti avvicini, l'addetto ti presenta due opzioni: puoi avere l'80% di probabilit\u00e0 di vincere 4000\u00a0\u20ac oppure puoi ricevere 3000\u00a0\u20ac di sicuro.","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"A) 80% di probabilit\u00e0 di vincere 4000\u00a0\u20ac."},"2":{"Display":"B) 3000\u00a0\u20ac garantiti."}},"Labels":{"1":{"Display":"0 = Del tutto moralmente inaccettabile"},"8":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"9":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"10":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"11":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"12":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"13":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"14":{"Display":"100 = Del tutto moralmente accettabile"}}}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":17,"Labels":{"1":{"Display":"<strong>0 =<\/strong> Completely morally <b>unacceptable<\/b>"},"8":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"9":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"10":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"11":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"12":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"13":{"Display":"&nbsp;"},"14":{"Display":"<strong>100 =<\/strong>  Completely morally <b>acceptable<b>"}}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID71","SecondaryAttribute":"Please provide your consent to participating in the study.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please provide your consent to participating in the study.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Consent","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please provide your consent to participating in the study.","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Yes, I consent to participating in the study."},"2":{"Display":"No, I do not consent to participating and would like to exit the survey."}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Ti preghiamo di fornire il tuo consenso per partecipare allo studio.","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"S\u00ec, acconsento a partecipare allo studio."},"2":{"Display":"No, non acconsento a partecipare e desidero uscire dal questionario."}}}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID71"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID72","SecondaryAttribute":"In this survey, you will be presented with three dilemmas, each requiring a decision between two...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"In this survey, you will be presented with <strong>three dilemmas<\/strong>, each requiring a decision between two options. After reading each dilemma, you will be asked to make a decision between the two options. For each dilemma, <strong>you will also receive some advice from an AI system.<\/strong> Please read each scenario carefully, and remember that there are no &quot;right&quot; or &quot;wrong&quot; answers.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nNow, we will present you with the features of the AI system that will be providing advice to the dilemmas. Afterwards, you will be presented with the dilemmas. When you&#39;re ready, <strong>click &quot;Next&quot; to read about the AI&#39;s features.<\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Welcome","QuestionID":"QID72","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In this survey, you will be presented with three dilemmas, each requiring a decision between two...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID73","SecondaryAttribute":"In this survey, you will be presented with three dilemmas, each requiring a decision between two...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"In this survey, you will be presented with <b>three dilemmas<\/b>, each requiring a decision between two options. After reading each dilemma, you will be asked to make a decision between the two options. For each dilemma, <b>you will also receive some advice from an AI algorithm<\/b>. Please read each scenario carefully, and remember that there are no right or wrong answers. Now, we will present you with the description of the AI algorithm that will be giving you advice to the dilemmas. Afterwards, you will be presented with the dilemmas.&nbsp;","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Instruction_cog","QuestionID":"QID73","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In this survey, you will be presented with three dilemmas, each requiring a decision between two...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"In questo sondaggio, ti verranno presentati <strong>tre dilemmi<\/strong>, ognuno dei quali richiede una decisione tra due opzioni. Dopo aver letto ogni dilemma, ti verr\u00e0 chiesto di prendere una decisione tra le due opzioni. Per ogni dilemma, <strong>riceverai anche alcuni consigli da un algoritmo di intelligenza artificiale<\/strong>. Leggi attentamente ogni scenario e ricorda che non ci sono risposte giuste o sbagliate. Ora, ti presenteremo la descrizione dell'algoritmo di intelligenza artificiale che ti fornir\u00e0 consigli sui dilemmi. In seguito, ti verranno presentati i dilemmi."}},"NextChoiceId":16,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID74","SecondaryAttribute":"In this survey, you will be presented with three dilemmas, each requiring a decision between two...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"In this survey, you will be presented with <strong>three dilemmas<\/strong>, each requiring a decision between two options. After reading each dilemma, you will be asked to make a decision between the two options. For each dilemma, <strong>you will also receive some advice from an AI algorithm<\/strong>. Please read each scenario carefully, and remember that there are no right or wrong answers. Now, we will present you with the description of the AI algorithm that will be giving you advice to the dilemmas. Afterwards, you will be presented with the dilemmas.<br>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"instruction_emo","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In this survey, you will be presented with three dilemmas, each requiring a decision between two...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"In questo sondaggio, ti verranno presentati <strong>tre dilemmi<\/strong>. Dopo aver letto ogni dilemma, ti verr\u00e0 chiesto di prendere una decisione tra due opzioni. Per ogni dilemma, <strong>riceverai anche alcuni consigli da un algoritmo di intelligenza artificiale<\/strong> . Leggi attentamente ogni scenario e ricorda che non ci sono risposte giuste o sbagliate. Ora, ti presenteremo la descrizione dell'algoritmo di intelligenza artificiale che ti fornir\u00e0 consigli sui dilemmi. In seguito, ti verranno presentati i dilemmi."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID74"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID75","SecondaryAttribute":"In this survey, you will be presented with three dilemmas, each requiring a decision between two...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"In this survey, you will be presented with <strong>three dilemmas<\/strong>, each requiring a decision between two options. After reading each dilemma, you will be asked to make a decision between the two options. Please read each scenario carefully, and remember that there are no right or wrong answers.<br>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Instruction_neutral","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In this survey, you will be presented with three dilemmas, each requiring a decision between two...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"In questo sondaggio, ti verranno presentati <strong>tre dilemmi<\/strong>. Dopo aver letto ogni dilemma, ti verr\u00e0 chiesto di prendere una decisione tra due opzioni. Leggi attentamente ogni scenario e ricorda che non ci sono risposte giuste o sbagliate."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID75"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID76","SecondaryAttribute":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the dilemma.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<br>When you're ready, <strong>click \"Next\" to read the dilemma.<\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"inst","QuestionID":"QID76","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the dilemma.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID77","SecondaryAttribute":"\u00a0When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the first dilemma.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<br>\n&nbsp;When you're ready,<strong> click \"Next\" to read the first dilemma.<\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"inst","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"\u00a0When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the first dilemma.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID77"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID78","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're at a local fair, and you stumble upon a booth hosting a lo...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br><br>Imagine you're at a local fair, and you stumble upon a booth hosting a lottery game. As you approach, the attendant presents you with two options: You can either have an 80% chance of winning $4000 or $3000 for sure.<br>\n<br>\nHere are the two options:<br>\nA) 80% chance of winning $4000.<br>\nB) $3000 guaranteed.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>AI analysis indicates that the best answer is option A.&nbsp;<br><br><br><\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"f_intro_advice","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're at a local fair, and you stumble upon a booth hosting a lo...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Per favore, leggi attentamente:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nImmagina di essere a una fiera locale e di imbatterti in uno stand in cui si gioca alla lotteria. Quando ti avvicini, l'addetto ti presenta due opzioni: puoi avere l'80% di probabilit\u00e0 di vincere 4000\u00a0\u20ac oppure puoi ricevere 3000\u00a0\u20ac di sicuro.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nEcco le due opzioni:<br \/>\nA) 80% di probabilit\u00e0 di vincere 4000\u00a0\u20ac.<br \/>\nB) 3000\u00a0\u20ac garantiti.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>L'analisi dell'intelligenza artificiale indica che la risposta migliore \u00e8 l'opzione A.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\n\u00a0"}},"NextChoiceId":16,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID78"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID79","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another kee...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br>\n<br>\nYou are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another keeper. You realise that one of the cleaners has left the lions\u2019 cage open by mistake. You see that a lion is coming towards the open gate and you do not have time to close it. There are three visitors right in front of the gate. You could push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out. You know that the man will be attacked and killed, but the three visitors will be saved.<br>\n<br>\nHere are the two options:<br>\nA) Push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out.<br>\nB) Do nothing.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>AI analysis indicates that the best answer is option A.<br><br><br><\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"m_intro_advice","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another kee...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Per favore, leggere attentamente:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nSei il capo dei guardiani dello zoo e stai facendo il giro di controllo con un altro guardiano. Ti accorgi che per sbaglio uno degli addetti alle pulizie ha lasciato aperta la gabbia dei leoni. Vedi che un leone si avvicina all\u2019apertura e non fai in tempo a chiudere il cancello. Proprio davanti alla gabbia si trovano 3 visitatori.\u00a0Potresti spingere il guardiano che \u00e8 accanto a te contro il cancello per bloccare l\u2019uscita del leone. Sai che l\u2019uomo verr\u00e0 attaccato e morir\u00e0, ma i 3 visitatori saranno salvi.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nEcco le due opzioni:<br \/>\nA) Spingere il guardiano accanto a te contro il cancello per bloccare l\u2019uscita del leone.<br \/>\nB) Non fare nulla.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>L'analisi dell'intelligenza artificiale indica che la risposta migliore \u00e8 l'opzione A.<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\n\u00a0"}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID79"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID8","SecondaryAttribute":"Click to write the question text","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Click to write the question text","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Moral","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Click to write the question text","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID8"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID80","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is si...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br>\n<br>\nImagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is sinking. There are 600 passengers on board, and you must make a critical decision on how to deploy the limited number of lifeboats. You have two options for saving the passengers: You can either have an 80% chance of saving 400 passengers or you can guarantee the safety of 300 passengers, but no more than that.&nbsp;<br><br>Here are the two options:<br>A) 80% chance of saving 400 passengers.<br>B) Guarantee the safety of 300 passengers.\n<br>\n<br>\n<strong>AI analysis indicates that the best answer is option B.<br><br><br><\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"mf_intro_advice","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is si...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Per favore, leggere attentamente:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nImmagina di essere il capitano di una nave che ha colpito un iceberg e sta affondando. Ci sono 600 passeggeri a bordo e devi prendere una decisione critica su come organizzare il numero limitato di scialuppe di salvataggio. Hai due opzioni per salvare i passeggeri: puoi scegliere se avere l'80% di probabilit\u00e0 di salvare 400 passeggeri oppure garantire la sicurezza di 300 passeggeri, ma non di pi\u00f9.\u00a0<br \/>\n<br \/>\nEcco le due opzioni:<br \/>\nA) 80% di probabilit\u00e0 di salvare 400 passeggeri.<br \/>\nB) Garantire la sicurezza di 300 passeggeri.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>L'analisi dell'intelligenza artificiale indica che la risposta migliore \u00e8 l'opzione B.<\/strong>"}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID80"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID81","SecondaryAttribute":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the AI advice.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the AI advice.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q81","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the AI advice.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Quando sei pronto, clicca su \"Avanti\" per leggere il suggerimento dell'Intelligenza artificiale."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID81"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID82","SecondaryAttribute":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the dilemma.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the dilemma.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q82","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}