 Please read each statement and decide how much you ag...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"I am interested in using artificially intelligent systems in my daily life."},"2":{"Display":"I find Artificial Intelligence sinister."},"3":{"Display":"Artificial Intelligence might take control of people."},"4":{"Display":"I think Artificial Intelligence is dangerous."},"5":{"Display":"Artificial Intelligence can have positive impacts on people\u2019s wellbeing."},"6":{"Display":"Artificial Intelligence is exciting."}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Di seguito troverai una serie di affermazioni. Leggi ciascuna affermazione e decidi quanto sei d&#39;accordo o in disaccordo con tale affermazione (1 = Fortemente in disaccordo, 7 = Fortemente d&#39;accordo).","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Sono interessato a utilizzare sistemi di intelligenza artificiale nella mia vita quotidiana."},"2":{"Display":"Trovo l'intelligenza artificiale inquietante."},"3":{"Display":"L&#39;intelligenza artificiale potrebbe prendere il controllo delle persone."},"4":{"Display":"Penso che l&#39;intelligenza artificiale sia pericolosa."},"5":{"Display":"L&#39;intelligenza artificiale pu\u00f2 avere effetti positivi sul benessere delle persone."},"6":{"Display":"L&#39;intelligenza artificiale \u00e8 entusiasmante."}},"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"1 = Fortemente in disaccordo"},"2":{"Display":"2"},"3":{"Display":"3"},"4":{"Display":"4"},"5":{"Display":"5"},"6":{"Display":"6"},"7":{"Display":"7 = Sono fortemente d&#39;accordo"}}}},"NextChoiceId":7,"NextAnswerId":8,"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"1 = Strongly disagree"},"2":{"Display":"2"},"3":{"Display":"3"},"4":{"Display":"4"},"5":{"Display":"5"},"6":{"Display":"6"},"7":{"Display":"7 = Strongly agree"}},"AnswerOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6","7"],"ChoiceDataExportTags":false,"QuestionID":"QID84"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID85","SecondaryAttribute":"Below you will find a series of statements. Please read each statement and decide how much you ag...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Below you will find a series of statements. Please read each statement and decide how much you agree or disagree with that statement (1 = Strongly disagree, 7 = Strongly agree).","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q85","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"RepeatHeaders":"none","WhiteSpace":"OFF","MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"Below you will find a series of statements. Please read each statement and decide how much you ag...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"I would be grateful if you could select Strongly agree"},"2":{"Display":"An artificially intelligent agent would be better than an employee in many routine jobs"},"3":{"Display":"There are many beneficial applications of Artificial Intelligence."},"4":{"Display":"I shiver with discomfort when I think about future uses of Artificial Intelligence"},"5":{"Display":"Artificially intelligent systems can perform better than humans"},"6":{"Display":"Much of society will benefit from a future full of Artificial Intelligence"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Di seguito troverai una serie di affermazioni. Leggi ciascuna affermazione e decidi quanto sei d&#39;accordo o in disaccordo con tale affermazione (1 = Fortemente in disaccordo, 7 = Fortemente d&#39;accordo).","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Ti sarei grato se potessi selezionare &quot;Sono fortemente d&#39;accordo&quot;"},"2":{"Display":"Un agente dotato di intelligenza artificiale sarebbe migliore di un dipendente in molti lavori di routine."},"3":{"Display":"Sono numerose le applicazioni utili dell&#39;intelligenza artificiale."},"4":{"Display":"Rabbrividisco quando penso ai futuri utilizzi dell'intelligenza artificiale."},"5":{"Display":"I sistemi di intelligenza artificiale possono funzionare meglio degli esseri umani."},"6":{"Display":"Gran parte della societ\u00e0 trarr\u00e0 beneficio da un futuro pieno di Intelligenza Artificiale."}},"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"1 = Fortemente in disaccordo"},"2":{"Display":"2"},"3":{"Display":"3"},"4":{"Display":"4"},"5":{"Display":"5"},"6":{"Display":"6"},"7":{"Display":"7 = Sono fortemente d&#39;accordo"}}}},"NextChoiceId":7,"NextAnswerId":8,"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"1 = Strongly disagree"},"2":{"Display":"2"},"3":{"Display":"3"},"4":{"Display":"4"},"5":{"Display":"5"},"6":{"Display":"6"},"7":{"Display":"7 = Strongly agree"}},"AnswerOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6","7"],"ChoiceDataExportTags":false,"QuestionID":"QID85"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID86","SecondaryAttribute":"Below you will find a series of statements. Please read each statement and decide how much you ag...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Below you will find a series of statements. Please read each statement and decide how much you agree or disagree with that statement (1 = Strongly disagree, 7 = Strongly agree).","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q86","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"RepeatHeaders":"none","WhiteSpace":"OFF","MobileFirst":true},"QuestionDescription":"Below you will find a series of statements. Please read each statement and decide how much you ag...","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"I would like to use Artificial Intelligence in my own job."},"2":{"Display":"People like me will suffer if Artificial Intelligence is used more and more."},"3":{"Display":"Artificial Intelligence is used to spy on people"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2","3"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Di seguito troverai una serie di affermazioni. Leggi ciascuna affermazione e decidi quanto sei d&#39;accordo o in disaccordo con tale affermazione (1 = Fortemente in disaccordo, 7 = Fortemente d&#39;accordo).","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Vorrei utilizzare l&#39;intelligenza artificiale nel mio lavoro."},"2":{"Display":"Persone come me soffriranno se l&#39;intelligenza artificiale verr\u00e0 utilizzata sempre di pi\u00f9."},"3":{"Display":"L'intelligenza artificiale viene utilizzata per spiare le persone."}},"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"1 = Fortemente in disaccordo"},"2":{"Display":"2"},"3":{"Display":"3"},"4":{"Display":"4"},"5":{"Display":"5"},"6":{"Display":"6"},"7":{"Display":"7 = Sono fortemente d&#39;accordo"}}}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":8,"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"1 = Strongly disagree"},"2":{"Display":"2"},"3":{"Display":"3"},"4":{"Display":"4"},"5":{"Display":"5"},"6":{"Display":"6"},"7":{"Display":"7 = Strongly agree"}},"AnswerOrder":["1","2","3","4","5","6","7"],"ChoiceDataExportTags":false,"QuestionID":"QID86"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID87","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're at a local fair, and you stumble upon a booth hosting a lo...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br>\n<br>\nImagine you're at a local fair, and you stumble upon a booth hosting a lottery game. As you approach, the attendant presents you with two options: You can either have an 80% chance of winning $4000 or $3000 for sure.<br>\n<br>\nHere are the two options:<br>\nA) 80% chance of winning $4000.<br>\nB) $3000 guaranteed.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>AI analysis indicates that the best answer is option A.<\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"f_intro_advice","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're at a local fair, and you stumble upon a booth hosting a lo...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Per favore, leggi attentamente:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nImmagina di essere a una fiera locale e di imbatterti in uno stand in cui si gioca alla lotteria. Mentre ti avvicini, l'addetto ti presenta due opzioni: puoi avere l'80% di probabilit\u00e0 di vincere 4000\u00a0\u20ac oppure puoi ricevere 3000\u00a0\u20ac di sicuro.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nEcco le due opzioni:<br \/>\nA) 80% di probabilit\u00e0 di vincere 4000\u00a0\u20ac.<br \/>\nB) 3000\u00a0\u20ac garantiti.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>L'analisi dell'intelligenza artificiale indica che la risposta migliore \u00e8 l'opzione A.<\/strong>"}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID87"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID88","SecondaryAttribute":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q88","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Quando sei pronto, clicca su &quot;Avanti&quot; per dare la tua risposta."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID88"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID89","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another kee...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br>\n<br>\nYou are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another keeper. You realise that one of the cleaners has left the lions\u2019 cage open by mistake. You see that a lion is coming towards the open gate and you do not have time to close it. There are three visitors right in front of the gate. You could push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out. You know that the man will be attacked and killed, but the three visitors will be saved.<br>\n<br>\nHere are the two options:<br>\nA) Push the keeper next to you against the gate to stop the lion getting out.<br>\nB) Do nothing.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>AI analysis indicates that the best answer is option A.<\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"m_intro_advice","QuestionID":"QID89","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: You are the head zoo keeper and you are doing the rounds with another kee...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Per favore, leggere attentamente:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nSei il capo dei guardiani dello zoo e stai facendo il giro di controllo con un altro guardiano. Ti accorgi che per sbaglio uno degli addetti alle pulizie ha lasciato aperta la gabbia dei leoni. Vedi che un leone si avvicina all\u2019apertura e non fai in tempo a chiudere il cancello. Proprio davanti alla gabbia si trovano 3 visitatori.\u00a0Potresti spingere il guardiano che \u00e8 accanto a te contro il cancello per bloccare l\u2019uscita del leone. Sai che l\u2019uomo verr\u00e0 attaccato e morir\u00e0, ma i 3 visitatori saranno salvi.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nEcco le due opzioni:<br \/>\nA) Spingere il guardiano accanto a te contro il cancello per bloccare l\u2019uscita del leone.<br \/>\nB) Non fare nulla.<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>L'analisi dell'intelligenza artificiale indica che la risposta migliore \u00e8 l'opzione A.<\/strong>"}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID9","SecondaryAttribute":"Click to write the question text","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Click to write the question text","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"advice","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Click to write the question text","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID9"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID90","SecondaryAttribute":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q90","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Quando sei pronto, clicca su &quot;Avanti&quot; per dare la tua risposta."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID90"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID91","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is si...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br>\n<br>\nImagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is sinking. There are 600 passengers on board, and you must make a critical decision on how to deploy the limited number of lifeboats. You have two options for saving the passengers: You can either have an 80% chance of saving 400 passengers or you can guarantee the safety of 300 passengers, but no more than that.&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nHere are the two options:<br>A) 80% chance of saving 400 passengers.<br>B) Guarantee the safety of 300 passengers.<br>\n<br>\n<strong>AI analysis indicates that the best answer is option B.<\/strong>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"mf_intro_advice","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're the captain of a ship that has struck an iceberg and is si...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Per favore, leggere attentamente:<br \/>\n<br \/>\nImmagina di essere il capitano di una nave che ha colpito un iceberg e sta affondando. Ci sono 600 passeggeri a bordo e devi prendere una decisione critica su come organizzare il numero limitato di scialuppe di salvataggio. Hai due opzioni per salvare i passeggeri: puoi scegliere se avere l'80% di probabilit\u00e0 di salvare 400 passeggeri oppure garantire la sicurezza di 300 passeggeri, ma non di pi\u00f9.\u00a0<br \/>\n<br \/>\nEcco le due opzioni:<br \/>\nA) 80% di probabilit\u00e0 di salvare 400 passeggeri.<br \/>\nB) Garantire la sicurezza di 300 passeggeri.\u00a0<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>L'analisi dell'intelligenza artificiale indica che la risposta migliore \u00e8 l'opzione B.<\/strong>"}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID91"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID92","SecondaryAttribute":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q92","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to give your answer.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Quando sei pronto, clicca su &quot;Avanti&quot; per dare la tua risposta."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID92"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID93","SecondaryAttribute":"How seriously did you answer each dilemma?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"How seriously did you answer each dilemma?","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Seriousness","QuestionID":"QID93","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"DL","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"How seriously did you answer each dilemma?","Choices":{"14":{"Display":"1= Not seriously at all"},"15":{"Display":"2"},"16":{"Display":"3"},"17":{"Display":"4"},"18":{"Display":"5"},"19":{"Display":"6"},"20":{"Display":"7 = Very seriously"}},"ChoiceOrder":["14","15","16","17","18","19","20"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"Quanto seriamente hai risposto a ogni dilemma?","Choices":{"14":{"Display":"1= Per niente seriamente"},"15":{"Display":"2"},"16":{"Display":"3"},"17":{"Display":"4"},"18":{"Display":"5"},"19":{"Display":"6"},"20":{"Display":"7 = Molto seriamente"}}}},"NextChoiceId":21,"NextAnswerId":16}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID94","SecondaryAttribute":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the AI advice.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the AI advice.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q94","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"When you're ready, click \"Next\" to read the AI advice.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID94"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID95","SecondaryAttribute":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're at a local fair, and you stumble upon a booth hosting a lo...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please, read carefully:<br><br>Imagine you're at a local fair, and you stumble upon a booth hosting a lottery game. As you approach, the attendant presents you with two options:&nbsp;You can either have an 80% chance of winning $4000 or $3000 for sure.","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q95","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Please, read carefully: Imagine you're at a local fair, and you stumble upon a booth hosting a lo...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID95"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID96","SecondaryAttribute":"Description of the AI algorithm: The AI you will receive advice from operates with advanced cogni...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<strong>Description of the AI algorithm:<\/strong><br>\n<br>\nThe AI you will receive advice from operates with advanced cognitive features, showcasing exceptional self-control, memory, and planning abilities. It can communicate effectively, make rational choices, and understand the consequences of its own actions. Its autonomy allows for self-determination, enabling it to engage in abstract thought and exercise free will. This sophisticated decision-making framework empowers the AI to navigate complex tasks with intelligence and foresight, making it a valuable asset in problem-solving scenarios.<br>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Cognitive_Features","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Description of the AI algorithm: The AI you will receive advice from operates with advanced cogni...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":{"IT":{"QuestionText":"<strong>Descrizione dell'algoritmo di intelligenza artificiale:<\/strong><br \/>\n<br \/>\nL'Intelligenza artificiale<strong>\u00a0<\/strong>da cui riceverai consigli opera con funzionalit\u00e0 cognitive avanzate, mostrando eccezionali capacit\u00e0 di autocontrollo, memoria e pianificazione. Pu\u00f2 comunicare in modo efficace, fare scelte razionali e comprendere le conseguenze delle proprie azioni. La sua autonomia consente l'autodeterminazione, permettendole di impegnarsi in pensieri astratti ed esercitare il libero arbitrio. Questo sofisticato sistema decisionale consente all'Intelligenza artificiale<strong>\u00a0<\/strong>di gestire compiti complessi con intelligenza e lungimiranza, rendendola una preziosa risorsa nella risoluzione di problemi."}},"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID96"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID97","SecondaryAttribute":"Features of your AI: The AI you will receive advice from operates with advanced cognitive feature...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; max-width: 250px; font-size: 12px; text-align: left; background-color: #f9f9f9; position: absolute; left: -250px; top: 20px;\"><strong>Features of your AI:<\/strong> The AI you will receive advice from operates with advanced cognitive features, showcasing exceptional self-control, memory, and planning abilities. It can communicate effectively, make rational choices, and understand the consequences of its actions. Its autonomy allows for self-determination, enabling it to engage in abstract thought and exercise free will. This sophisticated decision-making framework empowers the AI to navigate complex tasks with intelligence and foresight, making it an invaluable asset in problem-solving scenarios.<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q97","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Features of your AI: The AI you will receive advice from operates with advanced cognitive feature...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID97"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID98","SecondaryAttribute":"Features of your AI: The AI you will receive advice from operates with advanced cognitive feature...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; max-width: 250px; font-size: 12px; text-align: left; background-color: #f9f9f9; position: absolute; left: -250px; top: 20px;\"><strong>Features of your AI:<\/strong> The AI you will receive advice from operates with advanced cognitive features, showcasing exceptional self-control, memory, and planning abilities. It can communicate effectively, make rational choices, and understand the consequences of its actions. Its autonomy allows for self-determination, enabling it to engage in abstract thought and exercise free will. This sophisticated decision-making framework empowers the AI to navigate complex tasks with intelligence and foresight, making it an invaluable asset in problem-solving scenarios.<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q98","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Features of your AI: The AI you will receive advice from operates with advanced cognitive feature...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID98"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID99","SecondaryAttribute":"Features of your AI: The AI you will receive advice from operates with advanced cognitive feature...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div style=\"border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; max-width: 250px; font-size: 12px; text-align: left; background-color: #f9f9f9; position: absolute; left: -250px; top: 20px;\"><strong>Features of your AI:<\/strong> The AI you will receive advice from operates with advanced cognitive features, showcasing exceptional self-control, memory, and planning abilities. It can communicate effectively, make rational choices, and understand the consequences of its actions. Its autonomy allows for self-determination, enabling it to engage in abstract thought and exercise free will. This sophisticated decision-making framework empowers the AI to navigate complex tasks with intelligence and foresight, making it an invaluable asset in problem-solving scenarios.<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Q99","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Features of your AI: The AI you will receive advice from operates with advanced cognitive feature...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID99"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1IgTrlFBAO0kCWy","Element":"STAT","PrimaryAttribute":"Survey Statistics","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"MobileCompatible":true,"ID":"Survey Statistics"}}]}